CONGRATULATIONS are in order for musician and The Real Housewives of Durban star Londie London. She bought herself a Mercedes-Benz V Class bus. She announced the news on her Instagram account. The announcement was accompanied by a video clip showing her arriving in a G Class Mercedes-Benz before hopping into a new V Class Mercedes bus. Next to the bus there is a notice that reads: “Sorry I’m locked. I am waiting for my new owner, Miss Londiwe Zulu. V 300 F/Exclusive line. The best knows no alternative.” ALSO READ : BONNIE READY FOR THE SPOTLIGHT! She then captioned the clip as follows: “Imama malibe neBus.” The post has seen her fans and industry friends including Sorisha Naidoo, Nonto R, and Babes Wodumo congratulating her. Nthabi Shashi posted: “Imama is so gorgeous and deserves all the happiness in the world.” Shonisani wrote: “Congratulations Londi, it suits you so much.” Her friend, Nosipho Sibiya posted: “You know where I live girl, come pick me up. Congrats boo.” A post shared by Londie London (@londie_london_official) 